able sortable\"  width=\"100%\"\n!Frequency\n!Call sign\n!Branding\n!Format\n!Owner\n!Notes\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"AM 0650\" | AM 650\n|[[CISL (AM)|CISL]]\n| [[Sportsnet Radio|Sportsnet 650]]\n|[[Sports radio|Sports]]\n|[[Rogers Media]]\n|Licensed to [[Richmond, British Columbia|Richmond]]\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"AM 0690\" | AM 690\n|[[CBU (AM)|CBU]]\n|[[CBC Radio One]]\n|[[News]]/[[talk radio|talk]]\n|[[Canadian Broadcasting Corporation]]\n|\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"AM 0730\" | AM 730\n|[[CHMJ]]\n|AM 730\n|[[Highway advisory radio|All-traffic]]\n|[[Corus Entertainment]]\n|\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"AM 0980\" | AM 980\n|[[CKNW]]\n|Global News Radio 980 CKNW\n|News/talk\n|Corus Entertainment\n|\n|-\n|AM 1040\n|[[CKST]]\n|[[TSN Radio|TSN Radio 1040]]\n|Sports\n|[[Bell Media]]\n|\n|-\n|AM 1130\n|[[CKWX]]\n|News 1130\n|All-news\n|Rogers Media\n|\n|-\n|AM 1200\n|[[CJRJ]]\n|Spice Radio\n|Multicultural\n|IT Productions\n|\n|-\n|AM 1320\n|[[CHMB]]\n|AM1320 CHMB\n|Multicultural\n|Mainstream Broadcasting Corporation\n|\n|-\n|AM 1410\n|[[CFTE]]\n|[[Bloomberg Radio|BNN Bloomberg Radio 1410]]\n|[[Business news]]\n|Bell Media\n|\n|-\n|AM 1470\n|[[CJVB]]\n|[[Fairchild Radio]]\n|Multicultural\n|[[Fairchild Radio]]\n|\n|-\n|AM 1550\n|[[KRPI]]\n|Sher E Punjab\n|Multicultural\n|BBC Broadcasting\n|Licensed to [[Ferndale, Washington]], United States,  studios are in Richmond\n|-\n|AM 1600\n|[[KVRI]]\n|Radio India\n|Multicultural\n|[[Multicultural Broadcasting]]\n|Licensed to [[Blaine, Washington]], United States, studios are in [[Surrey, BC|Surrey]]\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"FM 088.1\" | FM 88.1\n|[[CBU (AM)|CBU-2-FM]]\n|CBC Radio One\n|News/talk\n|Canadian Broadcasting Corporation\n|FM translator for CBU 690 AM\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"FM 088.7\" | FM 88.7\n|[[CHNW-FM]]\n|CHNW\n|[[Emergency population warning|Emergency information]]\n|\n|Licensed to [[New Westminster]]\n|-\n| data-sort-value=\"FM 088.9\" | FM 88.9\n|VF2521\n|\n|[[Tourist information]]\n|Cameron Bell Consultancy\n|Lice